---
// src/components/AboutSection.astro
---
<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-brand-background dark:bg-brand-bg px-4">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold">The Player Behind The Game</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-primary dark:text-brand-primary mt-2">A little bit about me</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12">
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <div class="mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Who I Am</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-text-secondary dark:text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            A results-driven technology strategist and blockchain specialist combining technical expertise with business acumen. I have a proven ability to translate complex technical concepts into actionable business strategies while driving innovation and have led multiple cross-functional teams across the ASEAN region.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">My Skillset</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="skill-tag">Python</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Solidity</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Ethereum</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Smart Contracts</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Google Cloud</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">AWS</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Power BI</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Strategic Analysis</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Technical Leadership</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Data-Driven Decision Making</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Enterprise Architecture</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">My Journey</h3>
        <div class="relative border-l-2 border-brand-outline dark:border-brand-outline pl-6">
          <div class="mb-8 relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-8 top-1 w-4 h-4 bg-brand-primary rounded-full"></div>
            <p class="font-bold text-lg">Technology Strategy Researcher</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-text-secondary dark:text-brand-text-secondary">Independent Research (July 2023 - Present)</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-brand-text-primary dark:text-brand-text-primary">Conducted research on blockchain integration, resulting in two published papers. Developed frameworks for sustainable technology implementation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-8 relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-8 top-1 w-4 h-4 bg-brand-primary rounded-full"></div>
            <p class="font-bold text-lg">Blockhain Analyst (Investment and Technology)</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-text-secondary dark:text-brand-text-secondary">Cloudsolutely Pte. Ltd. (Nov 2022 - June 2023)</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-brand-text-primary dark:text-brand-text-primary">Spearheaded hybrid security architecture (MPC & Multisig). Executed investment strategies achieving 68% asset growth.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-8 relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-8 top-1 w-4 h-4 bg-brand-primary rounded-full"></div>
            <p class="font-bold text-lg">Assistant Lecturer</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-text-secondary dark:text-brand-text-secondary">Trisakti University (Aug 2020 - Aug 2022)</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-brand-text-primary dark:text-brand-text-primary">Designed learning modules for 5 core courses and developed a data science program using Python with 90% student satisfaction.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>